Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's...}Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{...not good!}...không ổn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{This is the finale.}Đây là kết thúc.
