Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He didn't stand a chance after all.}Không có lấy một cơ hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That was overwhelming.}Quá áp đảo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Macaron indeed is a true genius.}Macaron quả đúng là thiên tài.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Macaron didn't even need\Nto go all out to finish this match.}{\i0}Macaron còn chẳng cần dùng hết sức.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He disappeared?}Biến mất?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What the? They're suddenly buried!}Gì vậy? Tự nhiên bị chôn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What the hell is going on?}Chuyện quá gì đang xảy ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He emerged from underground!?}Cậu ta chui từ lòng đất lên?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You can't possibly have done that\Nso sound doesn't reverberate.}Không ngờ cậu làm vậy để âm thanh không vang đến.
